data.description: Move in ready- this home has been completely updated with a modern flair! Light and bright, your will love it here! The beautiful 7.3 acre lot is partially landscaped a great pergola, patio, and above ground pool in the backyard where private parties and BBQ's will be enjoyed. Partially fenced the yard feels completely private.  Bring the party inside to the modern finished lower level rec room. The lower level has an office space and a laundry, lots of modern storage and a half bath. The first floor has spacious bedrooms, a large kitchen, living room and dining room that leads to a large deck that overlooks the beautiful yard. Everything is done for you... Move right in and invite the guests.
